snippet: Tiger Woods celebrated his 41st birthday on Friday and long-time friend and fellow professional Notah Begay III predicts he will have more to celebrate in a triumphant return to the PGA Tour in 2017....
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods celebrated his 41st birthday on Friday and long-time friend and fellow professional Notah Begay III predicts he will have more to celebrate in a triumphant return to the PGA Tour in 2017.

headline.main: Woods Gets 'at Least One Win' Next Year, Says Begay
headline.print_headline: Woods Gets 'at Least One Win' Next Year, Says Begay
